  "elements": {
    "inscriptions": [
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "Linda Schultz",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 20
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 79.472,
          "y_px": -345
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "12.01.05 - 12.03.23",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 14
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 71.975,
          "y_px": -300
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "That your presence on this earth is felt by all.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 59.979,
          "y_px": -242
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "And the admiration for you is not small.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 46.484,
          "y_px": -214
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "Not by the things you say and do,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 40.486,
          "y_px": -192
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "But by everything that makes you, you.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 44.984,
          "y_px": -171.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "What words can be spoken to mend my heart?",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 55.48,
          "y_px": -148
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "Now that we are forever apart.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 17.994,
          "y_px": -124.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "There are no words that can stop these tears,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 35.987,
          "y_px": -102.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "Like watching the sun as it disappears.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 38.986,
          "y_px": -80.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "Words can be spoken, written and sung,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 35.987,
          "y_px": -57
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "And you will always be forever young.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 43.485,
          "y_px": -34.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "May it be known that you are in our hearts,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -185.934,
          "y_px": -7.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "While we watch the ship as it departs.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -215.924,
          "y_px": 16
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "You are now dancing with angels above.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -203.928,
          "y_px": 36.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "Peaceful and free with so much love.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -217.423,
          "y_px": 57
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "I do not wish to say the word goodbye,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -212.925,
          "y_px": 79
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "For I will miss you too much I will not lie.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -200.929,
          "y_px": 104
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-22",
        "text": "There are no words that one can say,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -224.921,
          "y_px": 126
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "To ease the pain and make it go away.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -221.922,
          "y_px": 148
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
        "text": "Instead you will live forever in my heart and mind.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -161.943,
          "y_px": 170
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "Go forth and shine and leave us behind.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -211.425,
          "y_px": 195
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-26",
        "text": "I will search for you in rainbows and stars,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -199.43,
          "y_px": 220
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-27",
        "text": "You will be the brightest one by far.\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -227.92,
          "y_px": 242
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "\"How much do you really mean to  me?",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 56.98,
          "y_px": -265.5
        },
